  "calendarNotes": "Fresno Unified begins the 2025–2026 school year on August 18, 2025 — earlier than most California districts, allowing the year to conclude before June's peak valley heat. Spring Break runs March 30–April 6, 2026. The school year ends June 11, 2026. Families relocating from districts that start after Labor Day should plan enrollment, childcare, and back-to-school shopping before mid-August.\n\nThe calendar includes California-specific no-school days — Lincoln's Birthday and Cesar Chavez Day — along with District Buyback Days when teachers attend professional development and students do not attend. The major multi-day breaks are Thanksgiving Break, Winter Break, and Spring Break; Fresno Unified does not have a Fall Break."
